<P>Two SERMONS Preach'd at the DEDICATION of the New Meeting-Hou&s;e on <HI>Church-Green BOSTON,</HI> the 8<HI>th</HI> of <HI>January</HI> 1716, 17.</P>
<P>By the Reverend Dr. <HI>COTTON MATHER,</HI> And the Reverend Mr. <HI>BENJAMIN WADSWORTH.</HI></P>
</DIV1>
